WEBVTT

00:04:59.640 --> 00:05:01.136
actually to delivering results,

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:03.240
if they don't know
if children are learning?

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:08.456
That's why the first big transformation

00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:10.256
before investing

00:05:10.280 --> 00:05:13.480
is to make the education system
deliver results.

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:18.896
Because pouring more money
into broken systems

00:05:18.920 --> 00:05:20.840
may only fund more inefficiencies.

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:24.056
And what deeply worries me --

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:27.296
if children go to school and don't learn,

00:05:27.320 --> 00:05:29.056
it devalues education,

00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:31.256
and it devalues spending on education,